{"tid":342991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一定係假新聞]韓女遊客醒來被對方壓住 日本民宿主人：只係摸下","createTime":"2017-08-01T05:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T03:04:28.000Z","uid":65429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a897d64ac81bd592ef635b9a337171f19529e70","tid":342991,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:36:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170717/56964907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170717%2F56964907&d=mVlYyMYxp8RAGMAxak8MbIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=f33cd190\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170717%2F56964907&h=78672d27\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170717/56964907</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓一名女子在日本福岡租住民宿時，遭民宿老闆強姦，疑犯被捕後否認有施暴，稱：「只是摸了一下」。<br />\n31歲受害人是上網預訂涉事的福岡市中央區民宿，當天與34歲民宿老闆長部聰一住在同一單位。事發在周日清晨6時半左右，睡醒張開眼時見長部壓在自己身上，涉嫌強姦她，亦令她身體受傷。受害人致電南韓駐福岡總領事館求助，總領事館亦向南韓警方報案。<br />\n疑犯因涉嫌強制性交致傷害罪被捕，但他否認指控，供稱：「我只是摸模而已，沒有強姦她。」<br />\n日本新聞網"},{"pid":"6239e957d6a45b4cd9b23d4c223e8322bbf21e48","tid":342991,"uid":65429,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"隻泡菜G, 老屈禾地偉大既大和民族國民, 其心可測<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c70b76100d9bb331e0deed6c2c1dde51572585a","tid":342991,"uid":65429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"垃圾蘋果亂報新聞, 影衰日本聲譽"},{"pid":"c0d123f8db0f18730a86c659f76fbc0b7218727a","tid":342991,"uid":65429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d536abbbd230b1d45b16771cf39937dfc47b1d98","tid":342991,"uid":89743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T06:02:45.000Z","msg":"總領事館亦向南韓警方報案。<img src=\"/assets